{"tid":1879360,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"當你錫緊你女朋友嘅時候，你係錫緊","createTime":"2020-02-14T07:14:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T07:25:57.000Z","uid":72962,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ecea2312e9b0b498e94b66d24b5a88b3880385b6","tid":1879360,"uid":72962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T07:14:44.000Z","msg":"assume 大家喺屋企都無防備得太好、無用公筷<br />\n而事實上都證明咗同居家人係極易傳染<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當你錫緊你女朋友嘅時候，你係錫緊佢，<br />\n仲有佢返過大陸嘅爸爸、<br />\n同親戚打牌嘅媽媽、<br />\n佢個哥哥、<br />\n佢哥哥個女朋友、<br />\n佢哥哥個女朋友個細佬、<br />\n佢哥哥個女朋友個細佬個男朋友<br />\n同埋佢哥哥個女朋友個細佬個男朋友個老豆etc<br />\n<br />\n如果大家唔想繼打邊爐家族之後成為接吻家族，希望大家諗清楚先咀落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cac9e10cf7ad0df4f6620939a0d2443661322676","tid":1879360,"uid":72962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T07:15:42.000Z","msg":"利申無女"},{"pid":"a30d8faa3958b8be219335b2e8f571de04363708","tid":1879360,"uid":266336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T07:24:38.000Z","msg":"有病毒的不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5aa4a9b90c80c38f00a663c4ffed9d9de9e0557","tid":1879360,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T07:25:57.000Z","msg":"好過你冇得錫"}]}